<plot>Insightful documentary about legendary low-budget film company Troma. The documentary follows Lloyd Kaufman, president of Troma Entertainment and creator of the Toxic Avenger, and his enthusiastic employees at the Cannes Film Festival during their 25th year of operation, famed to be the oldest truly independent film studio.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?618858</url></doc>
